<h2> Acknowledgement stage 2 (confirmation) Form </h2>
<p> Use this form to confirm a LETS payment.<p>
Input from this form is currently only accepted from the admin account.<p>
<form action="ack.cgi" method="post"> 
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="ac_id" VALUE="%s" >
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="pin" VALUE="%s" >
Payee/seller name (i.e. the name of the person being paid) *
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="to_name" VALUE="%s" SIZE="25" MAXLENGTH="40"><p>
Payee/seller account number/identifier. *
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="to_id" VALUE="%s" SIZE="4" MAXLENGTH="8"> <p>
Payer/buyer name. *
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="from_name" VALUE="%s" SIZE="25" MAXLENGTH="40"><p>
Payer/buyer account number/identifier. * 
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="from_id" VALUE="%s" SIZE="4" MAXLENGTH="8"> <p> 
Amount of payment *
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="amount" VALUE="%s" SIZE="8" MAXLENGTH="8"> <p>
Payment identifying details e.g. invoice no. or type of goods/services. *
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="details" VALUE="%s" SIZE="30" MAXLENGTH="40"><p>

<INPUT TYPE="submit" VALUE="Record Payment">  </form>  

